headline.print_headline: Bills to Legalize Medical Marijuana Introduced in Florida
headline.main: Bills to Legalize Medical Marijuana Introduced in Florida

lead_paragraph: Florida state legislators introduced identical bills on Monday to legalize medical marijuana treatment in the 2014 legislative session, in a bid to win approval before a constitutional amendment on the issue comes up for a public vote in November.
